data.description: Welcome to this beautiful quad style home where modern living meet convenience and style. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this home also features a newer water heater. a newer A/C as well as hardwood floors that add timeless elegance to every step. Enjoy the luxury of a fenced-in spacious backyard, perfect for relaxation and gardening. All appliances, including a new washer, are thoughtfully included.
